Adds the plugin architecture for verification skills (Feature 4.1), a pytest
test generator skill that reads spec contracts and produces tagged test files
(Feature 4.2), and tag coverage validation to ensure 100% spec ref coverage
in generated tests (Feature 4.3). Updates web UI to use skill dispatch instead
of the legacy generator, with tag validation step.

TDD: 18 new tests covering framework imports, skill registration, dispatch,
code generation, TestClient usage, spec ref coverage, and end-to-end generated
test execution against the dummy app. All 21 tests pass.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
